@*Welcome Banner*@
<div class="container-fluid p-5 bg-success text-white text-center">
    <h1>Welcome to GS Troop 41645 Page</h1>
    <p>We welcome all new members from rising Kindergarten through 12th Grade girls
        to join our multi-level Girl Scout troop. We are also looking for new parent 
        volunteers to help with all aspects of our troop.</p>
</div>
